{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"839bbaa33f","title":"国务院关于各地革命师生暂缓来京进行革命串连的通知","origin":"根据文件原件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"bce92f765c","index":0,"year":1966,"month":10,"day":15,"articleId":"839bbaa33f"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e36f85474f","type":"title","text":"国务院关于各地革命师生暂缓来京进行革命串联的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"839bbaa33f"},{"id":"684dd166f5","type":"appellation","text":"各中央局，各省、市、自治区党委、人委：","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"839bbaa33f"},{"id":"4138d04354","type":"paragraph","text":"外地来京革命师生现已超过百万，接待能力已达顶点，食宿、交通、卫生医疗等等都已发生极大困难。加之近来气温急剧下降，很多人不带被盖棉衣，极易生病。切盼各地革命师生暂缓来京，待现有的外地革命师生离京后，再按中共中央、国务院九月五日的通知有计划地来京进行革命串联。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"839bbaa33f"},{"id":"f336c84b60","type":"paragraph","text":" 国 务 院一九六六年十月十五日","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"839bbaa33f"}],"page":{"id":"dfc3c199ab","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"839bbaa33f","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}